CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 16, 1956, pg. A19 reads: "Class Of '24 - Allegheny High School's class of 1924 held its first big reunion at Gateway Plaza. At the head table, from the left, are George Norris, Mr. and Mrs. Edward Hough, Mr. and Mrs. Leroy Bannister, Dr. and Mrs. John pg. Schaefer and Harry E. Rau.  Mrs. Bannister was chairman. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of men and women gathered for Allegheny High School's class of 1924 reunion in Gateway Plaza
